Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.46,0:00:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今 我到底还能做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.31,0:00:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了改变那如狭隘庭园般的现实
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.85,0:00:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.29,0:00:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还活不到人生的一半
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.26,0:00:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反抗 相拥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.83,0:00:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在无意识中被刻上的经验纹身
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.30,0:00:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当站在悬崖边的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.47,0:00:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苦难抓住了我的手腕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.08,0:00:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次看到了自己的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.08,0:00:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前往更加宽广的领域\N往更深更大的某处
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.19,0:01:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝着无法预测的世界前进
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.13,0:01:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And lt's calling me again
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.84,0:01:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.97,0:01:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.16,0:02:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D-1的反应消失
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.74,0:02:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次的客人就招待到这儿了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.74,0:02:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作战结束
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.58,0:02:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,alpha各机返航
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.37,0:02:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫人真的非常努力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.16,0:02:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.54,0:02:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从战斗情况看，他已经不再迷惘了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.67,0:02:15.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不迷惘的人是不存在的，紫东大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.47,0:02:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结束了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.64,0:02:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.66,0:02:42.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.66,0:02:45.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好，有什么情况吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.24,0:02:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.45,0:02:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个月，MU也没什么动静
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.54,0:02:53.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔有寄到管理部的邮件，\N我就拿过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.46,0:02:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦你了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.84,0:02:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样和平的日子能维持下去就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.97,0:03:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太天真了，总一
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.97,0:03:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.97,0:03:08.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在您要下班了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.64,0:03:12.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要外出一天，这段时间里就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.85,0:03:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.27,0:03:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，功刀先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.57,0:03:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.07,0:03:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不找个女婿吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.78,0:03:20.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它是女孩子吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.74,0:03:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.87,0:03:33.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要外出，那，什么…MU…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.25,0:03:37.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MU大战死者联合悼念大会准备会
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.17,0:03:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对，就是这个，真绕口啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.55,0:03:44.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且，你一定要参加吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.76,0:03:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤其是对那些位高权重的人来说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.56,0:03:50.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉，对你来说…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.64,0:03:54.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天对你来说是个特别的日子，\N不要太严肃了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.56,0:03:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.65,0:04:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好困好困…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.24,0:04:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,olin
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.37,0:04:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,olin？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.24,0:04:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好，你去哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.74,0:04:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有东西忘在仁哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.25,0:04:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁？仁是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.37,0:04:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.87,0:04:18.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，为什么她叫你olin？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.17,0:04:19.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.05,0:04:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对女性而言…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.67,0:04:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礼物和男人的心，\N得到哪个会比较高兴？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.18,0:04:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道！别问我！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.64,0:04:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.64,0:04:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小惠，早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.97,0:04:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫人也好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.64,0:04:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.14,0:04:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问个问题，女性收到花或礼物之类的会很高兴吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.07,0:04:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是当然，谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.86,0:04:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是有绫人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.95,0:04:47.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑，谁会喜欢那种吃炸虾沾酱油的男人…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.07,0:04:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还不是用荷包蛋沾调味汁！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.45,0:04:53.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎哎，你们这群没有紧张感的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.46,0:04:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对MU作战的最前线就是这样啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.67,0:04:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好，各位！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.67,0:05:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天司令不在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.55,0:05:04.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我代行司令职责一天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.67,0:05:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那倒不错…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.68,0:05:09.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令不在的时候，不要出什么差错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.26,0:05:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令请假，还真是少见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.35,0:05:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起少见的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.98,0:05:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.64,0:05:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才不是遇到久远了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.65,0:05:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久远妹妹！她怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.44,0:05:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说忘了拿什么东西了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.65,0:05:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘了东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.57,0:05:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一个叫仁的人那里…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.15,0:05:27.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.36,0:05:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.45,0:05:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,职员中有这个家伙吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.95,0:05:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁，仁，仁…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.95,0:05:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们说什么呀？仁不是司令的名字嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.25,0:05:37.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.54,0:05:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.38,0:05:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.67,0:05:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.67,0:05:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.68,0:05:49.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,功刀仁，大家都不知道吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.18,0:05:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.47,0:05:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫人，树博士说有事找你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.35,0:05:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.27,0:05:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好\N各位安静一点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.94,0:06:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久远常常晚上到司令那边去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.36,0:06:03.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚…晚上！？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.94,0:06:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每周一两次左右
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.15,0:06:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每周一两次？！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.07,0:06:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人真是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.24,0:06:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的，我就去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.58,0:06:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫你去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.58,0:06:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，他说有一些有趣的东西问我要不要去看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.87,0:06:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有趣的东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.17,0:06:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小惠，能带绫人去如月博士哪里吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.46,0:06:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包在我身上，少佐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.06,0:06:39.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过，她为什么总在本部进出呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.64,0:06:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.06,0:06:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是说久远，她既不是职员也不是军人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.15,0:06:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她和绫人一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.28,0:06:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫人虽然是平民，\N但他具有操纵RahXephon的奇异能力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.37,0:06:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以认为久远是以这类方式来协助TERRA的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.25,0:07:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然每天面对着乐谱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.88,0:07:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但和我最喜欢的小提琴在一起\N我感到生活很充实
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.84,0:07:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不能经常和爸爸见面，有些寂寞…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.76,0:07:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说下次我演出时您一定会来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.26,0:07:16.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到那时，我有礼物要送给爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.35,0:07:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您一定会开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.27,0:07:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以，一定要来噢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.06,0:07:25.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很期待爸爸能来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.24,0:07:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有趣的东西就是这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.37,0:07:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.45,0:07:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在听什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.37,0:07:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个月，久远演奏的小提琴曲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.66,0:07:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久远？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.54,0:07:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将乐曲录音后，在发芽阶段持续播放
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.67,0:07:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开出了和原始品种有点像又不完全像的花
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.55,0:07:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便说一句，那边的是原始品种
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.26,0:07:53.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这边的花朵更多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.55,0:07:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我问过久远，\N不过她说并不是有意这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.56,0:07:59.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.97,0:08:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉到什么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.15,0:08:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这么回事啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.65,0:08:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…还是不对…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.57,0:08:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.86,0:08:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着听着就会悲伤起来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.87,0:08:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很美的曲子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.87,0:08:21.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…怎么说呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.37,0:08:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不协调…对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.96,0:08:27.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有不协调的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.35,0:09:20.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您检查一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.85,0:09:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个真不错！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.98,0:09:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是巧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.65,0:09:28.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给谁的礼物？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.86,0:09:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了，谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.86,0:09:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好，也让我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.44,0:09:36.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,功刀先生，这位是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.07,0:09:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是朋友，要同样款式的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.37,0:09:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.37,0:09:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.45,0:09:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,个，十，百，千，万…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.16,0:09:47.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.25,0:09:52.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请…请等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.55,0:09:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久远！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.26,0:09:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来后，睡过一会儿了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.18,0:10:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不够
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.47,0:10:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.97,0:10:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不够
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.85,0:10:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被切断的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.77,0:10:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法吹及的风
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.27,0:10:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能啮合的齿轮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.27,0:10:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么地方不对…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.44,0:10:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.65,0:10:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,olin也说过了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.44,0:10:14.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,olin也…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.36,0:10:17.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的，我让他听的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.65,0:10:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也说过同样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.36,0:10:21.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,olin和久远很相似…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.08,0:10:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁没问题吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.45,0:10:26.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样没关系吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.46,0:10:31.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这是她的意愿，也就是说他选择了直接面对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.67,0:10:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思，让你陪我买送给侄女的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.47,0:10:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这方面我是不太懂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.34,0:10:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.55,0:10:43.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用那么着急吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.64,0:10:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离开船还有一段时间
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.56,0:10:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亘理先生今天…那个…MU…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.44,0:10:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MU大战死者联合悼念大会准备会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.07,0:11:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对，就是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.66,0:11:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他去那里了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.74,0:11:05.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开悼念会是可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.87,0:11:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过，在这之前不是还有另一件事应该处理好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.75,0:11:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.04,0:11:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面对突然袭来的MU首先发动攻击的是当时的驻日美军
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.67,0:11:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这个原因，现在的美国已经没有往日的威风了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.26,0:11:24.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是悲惨啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.47,0:11:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.85,0:11:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传闻说是美军独断专行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.77,0:11:34.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实际上真正的操纵者另有其人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.65,0:11:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙是当时国防部的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.07,0:11:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙让部下承担责任后就行踪不明了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.74,0:11:47.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被诬陷的人是个好心肠
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.66,0:11:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且，据说是个很有前途的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.25,0:11:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事还有下文
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.75,0:12:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对MU使用战术核武器的人是这个部下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.76,0:12:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他本人也不知道那是核弹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.64,0:12:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是当然的，这个国家应该没有核弹的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.97,0:12:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过，就因为这样，城市却被完全摧毁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.35,0:12:14.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什么感想？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.77,0:12:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还在犹豫什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.07,0:12:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是，那里还有来不及逃走的平民
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.86,0:12:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.57,0:12:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心，这是对敌人的精确打击
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.45,0:12:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.24,0:12:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是军人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.58,0:12:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是军人的话，就要绝对服从上司的命令！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.17,0:12:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,功刀先生应该也在国防部服过役吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.18,0:12:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过去是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.47,0:12:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2013年辞职的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.26,0:12:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直想问你…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.77,0:12:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么不做重新整编后的统合自卫队的司令
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.64,0:12:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是做了TERRA的司令呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.77,0:12:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为待遇上的差别吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.28,0:13:02.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只能给我的侄女买这些东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.45,0:13:05.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么好工作吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.36,0:13:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是我工作的地方，倒是可以帮你介绍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.24,0:13:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在TERRA？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.37,0:13:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，地球联合
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.67,0:13:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被你狠狠地将了一军
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.84,0:13:23.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，我不陪你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.84,0:13:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请请，浪费了你这么多时间，不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.85,0:13:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙是想赎罪吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.14,0:13:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是战争傻瓜啊，是不是，松鼠先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.15,0:13:45.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要走了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.36,0:13:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的，怎么硬塞给我们这些东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.87,0:13:54.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦~两位，工作结束了在约会？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.66,0:13:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.04,0:13:57.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.75,0:13:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉，打扰了你们了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.75,0:14:02.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别…别开玩笑，只是收了如月博士的花，所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.05,0:14:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花？树给的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.76,0:14:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，所以我想去买花瓶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.76,0:14:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是帮忙拿东西的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.97,0:14:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别乱指！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.06,0:14:15.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是两个女人一起去吃烧肉了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.06,0:14:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.27,0:14:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.35,0:14:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾尔菲今天好像没喝酒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.44,0:14:27.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫人·神名
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.36,0:14:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.24,0:14:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.08,0:14:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吗？功刀司令的名字叫仁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.95,0:14:36.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.87,0:14:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.87,0:14:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.38,0:14:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然吗，说得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.96,0:14:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.67,0:14:45.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.34,0:14:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为，今天司令难得请假
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.76,0:14:53.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家多多少少都在谈论这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.35,0:14:56.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.06,0:15:01.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠，今天对司令来说是特别的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.94,0:15:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什么都知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.65,0:15:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你挺有两下子嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.45,0:15:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在东京时我可是经常玩这个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.87,0:15:15.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自那以后的四个月
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.45,0:15:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对RahXephon的操纵已经比较自如了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.46,0:15:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.54,0:15:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过，你不是军人！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.97,0:15:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游戏结束，游戏结束
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.18,0:15:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…你打算驾驶它到什么时候？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.27,0:15:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，忘记买花瓶了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.56,0:15:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要回去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.15,0:15:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了…没关系…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.07,0:15:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去看船吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.66,0:15:54.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.45,0:15:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.58,0:15:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.37,0:16:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇，真豪华！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.04,0:16:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是环岛航行的水上餐厅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.04,0:16:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在非常流行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.67,0:16:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.55,0:16:11.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟，两位，在约会吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.97,0:16:13.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说过了不是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.18,0:16:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.55,0:16:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…为什么你会在这种地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.77,0:16:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点事…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.77,0:16:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管这个，说起约会…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.44,0:16:29.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,功刀先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.94,0:16:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别的一天，是指约会吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.74,0:16:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也不错，约会的对象是她的女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.16,0:16:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女儿？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.58,0:16:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,功刀先生已经结婚了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.37,0:16:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是女儿的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.17,0:16:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.26,0:16:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是老样子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.55,0:16:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红色的Mouton-Rothschild
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.55,0:16:58.35,*note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Mouton-Rothschild：一种法国葡萄酒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.85,0:16:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只知道这种酒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.27,0:17:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你不想知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.77,0:17:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃饭吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.15,0:17:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经吃过了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.15,0:17:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会接受邀请你是不是很吃惊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.28,0:17:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.65,0:17:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看过录像带了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.45,0:17:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.86,0:17:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感想呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.37,0:17:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子很有前途
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.37,0:17:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有很高的天赋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.17,0:17:27.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的罪过
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.17,0:17:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.96,0:17:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.26,0:17:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以工作为借口不和她见面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.34,0:17:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.97,0:17:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像你说得一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.14,0:17:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我接受你的邀请，\N因为我就要离开日本了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.15,0:17:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.28,0:17:54.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字也要改了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.95,0:17:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.67,0:18:08.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然没有放进上次的信里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.38,0:18:10.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这最后一段
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.25,0:18:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最终还是决定把它交给你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.55,0:18:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这是那孩子一边\N想念着你一边谱写的曲子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.06,0:18:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…感觉能读懂吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.14,0:18:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…因为我是个不求甚解的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.06,0:18:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.24,0:18:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,功刀先生，刚刚有人送来的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.53,0:18:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和女孩子见面时应该准备鲜花 司令官\N——小喽罗代表+1敬上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.66,0:18:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能给我看看吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.17,0:18:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是给你的花
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.26,0:18:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我差不多该走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.76,0:19:00.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.85,0:19:04.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真理子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.56,0:19:10.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.07,0:19:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道司令和女儿约会成功了没有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.87,0:19:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉我们是在多管闲事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.58,0:19:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么啊！女孩子的心情只有我这个女孩子懂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.96,0:19:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.17,0:19:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之父母与孩子之间的事，\N外人是不会明白的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.47,0:19:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，烦死了烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.84,0:19:43.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回去做饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.64,0:19:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我肚子饿了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.97,0:19:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.77,0:19:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Alpha1，申请发射许可
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.85,0:19:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.94,0:19:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来挺可靠的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.44,0:19:59.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了能够不依赖普通平民，是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.07,0:20:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.97,0:20:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能看看这个吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.14,0:20:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
